{
  "stem": "18486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 370.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But by that time, we had a lot of Jewish people in our house, already, hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they begged my husband and me not to wear that star, because they said you'd attract attention to yourself with that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We took it off again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I have never seen it myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my husband went off into Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived in the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when my husband went to Amsterdam, he always came home all shook up, and pale and miserable from what he had seen there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he had seen Jewish people being thrown in-- in open animal carts from the train, you know, and-- you know, and--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband was an agriculturist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he-- what did he actually do in the war?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did nothing but trying to find food for his family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And afterwards, he-- well, after the war, we came to America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, we had a children's home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for the first time, I had fear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we started immediately to be very active to help the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that-- that included, also, a lot of fear, of course, and danger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So our life-- our life changed very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were in need of help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's like when you see a child fall in the water, you jump in and get it out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't, because I can't swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But-- but every other decent people will do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had Jewish friends and.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We heard about all that-- all the laws that came out to the Jews, so we said we'll help them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it started out with the child.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
